sequenceDiagram
    actor SA as Superadmin
    participant API as POST /api/admin/orgs
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    actor CLI as Cliente (terminal)
    participant OT as GET /api/onboarding/token

    SA->>API: nome, slug, n8nSlug
    API->>DB: INSERT organization
    API->>DB: INSERT onboarding_token (SHA-256, expira 7d)
    API-->>SA: onboardingToken pruma_ot_xxx

    SA-->>CLI: envia token por Slack/e-mail

    CLI->>CLI: make setup TOKEN=pruma_ot_xxx
    CLI->>OT: GET /api/onboarding/pruma_ot_xxx
    OT->>DB: lookup SHA-256(token)
    OT->>DB: valida expiresAt e usedAt IS NULL
    OT->>DB: UPDATE usedAt = now() (token queimado)
    OT-->>CLI: organizationSlug, n8nSecret, apiUrl
    CLI->>CLI: escreve .pruma-secrets e pruma.json
    CLI->>API: make deploy - workflows registrados
